Breaking Bad takes the TV shows to next level 1.Screenplay&Direction:Best. There are some scenes that are technically so sound that you will be amazed.But sometimes the pace is slow but it is worth it 2.Cast&Characterization:It is a perfectly assembled cast.Performances by all the cast is so good especially by Bryan Cranston, Aaron Paul, Dean Norris, Bob Odenkirk. The characterizations are awesome. To how much lengths Walter White goes to save his family is simply moving. 3.BGM:In some scenes there is only silence which represents a slow paced scene. Title theme is awesome.4.Story:The plot is the main part of breaking bad that makes it so good. There are no loose ends in the series and no unnecessary sub plots or characters. To sum this up this is a MUST WATCH show for everyone